<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1903-03-23T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1903-03-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="558" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d558">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Combs</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Guatemala</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-03-23"><hi rend="italic">March 23,
                                1903</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>(Mr. Combs reports that the Government of Guatemala, in maintaining its
                            constitution, refuses to recognize the American citizenship of Alberto,
                            Posadas, a native-born Guatemalan returning bearing a United States
                            passport, and that the naturalized citizen referred to is under
                            detention for refusal to pay a forced loan.</p>
                        <p>Mr. Combs requests instructions.)</p>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>